casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Riggenbach, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Riggenbach, 128 Ohio St.3d 338, 2010-Ohio-6336.]

(No. 2010-1532 Submitted December 14, 2010 Decided December 29, 2010.) Shane Riggenbach, pro se.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on the authority of State v. Fischer, 128 Ohio St.3d 92, 2010-Ohio-6238, 942 N.E.2d 332.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, and Cupp, JJ., concur. Lanzinger, J., dissents.
